p: Univariate analysis of variance (ANOVA) analysis of all quantitative data (P < 0.05), followed by the Duncan multiple range test, expressed as mean ± standard deviation (SD) (SPSS 22.0, SPSS Inc., Chicago, IL), USA). All experiments were performed in triplicate, using three lots of different films. All figures drawn using OriginPro 9.0 (OriginLab Co., Northampton, MA, USA). The datasets generated and/or analyzed during the current study are available from the corresponding author on reasonable request.
